│ to add a type-and-length guard inside FoldOpIntoSelect itself: only fold when the select result type equals the op result type and, for vector types, the condition vector length        │
│ matches the result vector length. This prevents the invalid SelectInst creation generically and should satisfy tests that expect no fold for mismatched/widening cases while allowing    │
│ valid same-length folds elsewhere.                                                                                                                                                       │
